    "description": "Last Minute is a single-player first-person story game set in the woods.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nLife was getting pretty tough for you in the city, you just lost your job and the constant outside city-noise has been disturbing you a lot. You decided it‘s best if you move out with the dog you care about the most, somewhere peaceful and quiet – into the woods.<br />\r\nShortly after setting in the woods, something disastrous happens. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nNote: Last Minute is a video game that includes minimal violence. The game is suitable for children 13 and over.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nKey features:<br />\r\n<br />\r\n-Calm, emotional story that lasts 1 hour.<br />\r\n-Amazing soundtrack that illustrates current events.<br />\r\n-Detailed, lush wilderness environment",
